Initialize a new clash policy with a safe default configuration

Usage: init [OPTIONS] [SCOPE]

Arguments:
  [SCOPE]  Scope to initialize: "user" (global) or "project" (this repo)

Options:
      --no-bypass [<NO_BYPASS>]  Skip setting bypassPermissions in Claude Code settings [possible
                                 values: true, false]
  -h, --help                     Print help (see more with '--help')
